---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="X-VERSE｜Web 3Dプラットフォーム">
    <Header currentService="top" />

    <div class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 via-white to-slate-50"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-1/2 bg-xverse-red/100/5 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <main>
        <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 pt-20">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
                <video autoplay muted loop playsinline class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60">
                    <source src="/assets/video/hero_demo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                </video>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-black/50 to-black/70"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto py-20">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="hero-logo">
                        <img src="/assets/images/logo_w.svg" alt="X-VERSE" class="h-10 md:h-12 mx-auto" />
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-white">
                        <span class="block hero-title-1">世界を3Dで</span>
                        <span class="block mt-2 text-xverse-red hero-title-2">シミュレートし体験する</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed hero-text">
                        X-VERSEは、Webブラウザだけで現実の空間・時間・動きを扱える<br>
                        次世代Web3Dプラットフォームです。<br>
                        <span class="text-xverse-red-light font-semibold">倉庫、建設、不動産・都市開発、防災、体験</span>を一つの基盤に統合します。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="#concept" class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-20 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 hero-scroll cursor-pointer hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-300">
                <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase font-light">Scroll</span>
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
                </svg>
            </a>

            <style>
                @keyframes hero-fade-in {
                    from {
                        opacity: 0;
                        transform: translateY(40px);
                        filter: blur(10px);
                    }
                    to {
                        opacity: 1;
                        transform: translateY(0);
                        filter: blur(0);
                    }
                }

                @keyframes hero-title-reveal {
                    0% {
                        opacity: 0;
                        transform: translateY(100px) rotateX(30deg);
                        filter: blur(20px);
                    }
                    60% {
                        filter: blur(5px);
                    }
                    100% {
                        opacity: 1;
                        transform: translateY(0) rotateX(0);
                        filter: blur(0);
                    }
                }

                @keyframes hero-text-reveal {
                    from {
                        opacity: 0;
                        transform: translateY(30px);
                        filter: blur(5px);
                    }
                    to {
                        opacity: 1;
                        transform: translateY(0);
                        filter: blur(0);
                    }
                }

                .hero-logo {
                    opacity: 0;
                    animation: hero-fade-in 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.5s forwards;
                }

                .hero-title-1 {
                    opacity: 0;
                    animation: hero-title-reveal 2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 2.2s forwards;
                }

                .hero-title-2 {
                    opacity: 0;
                    animation: hero-title-reveal 2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 3.5s forwards;
                }

                .hero-text {
                    opacity: 0;
                    animation: hero-text-reveal 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 5.5s forwards;
                }

                .hero-scroll {
                    opacity: 0;
                    animation: hero-fade-in 1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 7s forwards;
                }
            </style>
        </section>

        <section id="concept" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative bg-white overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 mb-20">
                <div class="text-center space-y-6 animate-on-scroll">
                    <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-xverse-red uppercase font-bold">Concept</p>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">「現実」を、そのまま<br class="hidden md:block">3Dで扱う</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                        X-VERSEは、単なる3D表示ツールではありません。<br class="hidden md:block">
                        現実世界をベースに、<span class="text-xverse-red font-semibold">配置・操作・時間変化・共有</span>までをWeb上で完結させます。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 stagger-container">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">01</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">Space</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">空間</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">地形・建物・内部構造まで3Dで扱い、現実の理解と共有を高速化。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">02</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">Time</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">時間</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">日時・工程・移動・変化を時系列で再現し、計画・検証・教育に活用。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">03</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">Action</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">操作</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">配置、スケール調整、磁石連結UI、アニメーション、VRなどを統合。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">04</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">Share</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">共有</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">URL共有・同時操作。クラウド／ローカル／イントラ運用も選択可能。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">05</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">Camera</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">視点体験</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">車窓・座席目線・上空など、視点を固定して"体験"として見せられる。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-xverse-red transition-colors shrink-0">
                                <span class="text-xverse-red font-mono text-xs font-bold group-hover:text-white transition-colors">06</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-xverse-red tracking-widest mb-1 uppercase">AI</h4>
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">3D生成</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">画像と指示から3Dモデルを生成し、配置・検証・説明をスピード化。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="platform-section" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
                    <div class="space-y-10 platform-slide-left">
                        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-xverse-red uppercase font-bold">Platform</p>
                        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-slate-900">なぜ、X-VERSEは<br class="hidden md:block">「基盤」なのか</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                            <p>X-VERSEは、準日本製のWebGLベースの当社独自の汎用3Dライブラリです。</p>
                            <p>動作環境はWebブラウザをベースに、クラウドやElectronでのローカル操作に対応し、ライブラリのインストールは不要です。</p>
                            <p>3Dモデルのインポートはもちろん、CAD知識なしで3Dパーツを組み上げて構造物を簡単に造る仕組みも取り入れています。</p>
                            <p>また、用途ごとに必要となる3D活用を「空間 × 時間 × 操作 × 共有」という共通要素で統合する。それがX-VERSEの設計思想です。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-1 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden platform-slide-right">
                        <div class="bg-slate-950 p-4 border-b border-white/10 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-xverse-red/100"></span>
                                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
                                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase ml-4">Architecture.js</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-8 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto min-h-[280px]" id="code-typewriter"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative bg-white overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-6 animate-on-scroll">
                    <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-xverse-red uppercase font-bold">Library</p>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">X-VERSEライブラリの特徴</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                        X-VERSEは、3D地図上へのモデル配置を含め、必要機能を<span class="text-xverse-red font-semibold">プラットフォームとして内包</span>。<br class="hidden md:block">
                        「ライブラリの寄せ集め」ではなく、Web3D専用の統合基盤です。
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 stagger-container">
                    <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-xverse-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">基本機能</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>Photorealistic 3D Maps上に3Dモデルを直接配置</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>日影・日照をリアルタイム計算</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>タイムライン制御（移動・工程・変化）</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>3Dアニメーション・カメラ連動</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-xverse-red/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-xverse-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">操作・制作</h3>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>磁石連結UIで3D部品を直感的に組み上げ</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>3Dモデルのスケール調整・取り込み</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>生成AIで3Dモデル作成・配置</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-xverse-red mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div><span>VRデバイス対応</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="use-cases" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative bg-white overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
                <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-6 animate-on-scroll">
                    <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] text-xverse-red uppercase font-bold">Use Cases</p>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">適用可能な業務例</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">X-VERSEは<span class="text-xverse-red font-semibold">「Webで実務に落ちる」</span>ことを重視。さまざまな業界で3D活用を推進します。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 stagger-container">
                    <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="text-xverse-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">倉庫・物流レイアウト</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">磁石連結UIでラックや設備を配置。作業動線のシミュレーションと共有を容易に。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="text-xverse-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">建設工程シミュレーション</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">タイムライン制御で施工ステップを可視化。日影や資材配置の検証を多人数で同時に実施。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="text-xverse-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">不動産・都市開発</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">3D都市モデル上での将来イメージ投影。車窓・座席目線（CAMERA）による景観体験の提供。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="text-xverse-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">防災シミュレーション</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">避難経路や災害時の動線を3Dで可視化。時間軸を使った避難訓練シナリオの検証にも対応。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-xverse-red/30 hover:bg-xverse-red/10 transition-all duration-300 group stagger-item card-tilt">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-4">
                            <div class="text-xverse-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shrink-0">
